<p>1.进入文件夹启动sdk</p>

<pre>
<code>cd&nbsp; /workspace/coding_tools/android_studio/android-studio/bin</code></pre>

<pre>
<code>./studio.sh</code></pre>

<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>

<p>2.创建app,选择java版本，不使用kt文件</p>

<p>3.增加依赖，安装：</p>

<pre>
<code>dependencies {
    <span style="color:#d4d0ab">// 网络请求库</span>
    implementation <span style="color:#abe338">&#39;com.squareup.okhttp3:okhttp:4.9.1&#39;</span>
 
    <span style="color:#d4d0ab">// JSON解析库</span>
    implementation <span style="color:#abe338">&#39;com.google.code.gson:gson:2.8.8&#39;</span>
}</code></pre>

<p>如果没有安装成功会提示：</p>

<pre>
<code>Cannot <span style="color:#f5ab35">resolve</span> symbol <span style="color:#abe338">&#39;Gson&#39;</span>
Cannot <span style="color:#f5ab35">resolve</span> symbol <span style="color:#abe338">&#39;okhttp3</span></code></pre>

<p>修改 <code>MainActivity.java文件：（增加）</code></p>

<pre>
<code><span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> android.os.AsyncTask;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> android.os.Bundle;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> android.util.Log;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> androidx.appcompat.app.AppCompatActivity;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> com.google.gson.Gson;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> okhttp3.OkHttpClient;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> okhttp3.Request;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> okhttp3.Response;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> org.json.JSONArray;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> org.json.JSONException;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> org.json.JSONObject;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> java.io.IOException;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> java.util.ArrayList;
<span style="color:#dcc6e0">import</span> java.util.List;

<span style="color:#dcc6e0">public</span> <span style="color:#dcc6e0">class</span> <span style="color:#00e0e0">MainActivity</span> <span style="color:#dcc6e0">extends</span> <span style="color:#00e0e0">AppCompatActivity</span> {

    <span style="color:#dcc6e0">private</span> <span style="color:#dcc6e0">static</span> <span style="color:#dcc6e0">final</span> String API_URL = <span style="color:#abe338">&quot;https://admin.linlin.fun/api/v1/blogs&quot;</span>;

    <span style="color:#f5ab35">@Override</span>
    <span style="color:#dcc6e0">protected</span> <span style="color:#dcc6e0">void</span> <span style="color:#00e0e0">onCreate</span><span style="color:#f5ab35">(Bundle savedInstanceState)</span> {
        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">super</span>.onCreate(savedInstanceState);
        setContentView(R.layout.activity_main);

        <span style="color:#d4d0ab">// 执行异步任务来获取博客列表</span>
        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">new</span> FetchBlogsTask().execute();
    }

    <span style="color:#dcc6e0">private</span> <span style="color:#dcc6e0">class</span> <span style="color:#00e0e0">FetchBlogsTask</span> <span style="color:#dcc6e0">extends</span> <span style="color:#00e0e0">AsyncTask</span>&lt;<span style="color:#00e0e0">Void</span>, <span style="color:#00e0e0">Void</span>, <span style="color:#00e0e0">List</span>&lt;<span style="color:#00e0e0">Blog</span>&gt;&gt; {

        <span style="color:#f5ab35">@Override</span>
        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">protected</span> List&lt;Blog&gt; <span style="color:#00e0e0">doInBackground</span><span style="color:#f5ab35">(Void... voids)</span> {
            OkHttpClient client = <span style="color:#dcc6e0">new</span> OkHttpClient();
            Request request = <span style="color:#dcc6e0">new</span> Request.Builder()
                    .url(API_URL)
                    .build();

            <span style="color:#dcc6e0">try</span> {
                Response response = client.newCall(request).execute();
                String jsonData = response.body().string();
                <span style="color:#dcc6e0">return</span> parseJsonData(jsonData);
            } <span style="color:#dcc6e0">catch</span> (IOException e) {
                e.printStackTrace();
            }

            <span style="color:#dcc6e0">return</span> <span style="color:#dcc6e0">null</span>;
        }

        <span style="color:#f5ab35">@Override</span>
        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">protected</span> <span style="color:#dcc6e0">void</span> <span style="color:#00e0e0">onPostExecute</span><span style="color:#f5ab35">(List&lt;Blog&gt; blogs)</span> {
            <span style="color:#dcc6e0">if</span> (blogs != <span style="color:#dcc6e0">null</span>) {
                <span style="color:#d4d0ab">// 在这里使用博客列表做你想要的展示操作</span>
                <span style="color:#dcc6e0">for</span> (Blog blog : blogs) {
                    Log.d(<span style="color:#abe338">&quot;Blog&quot;</span>, blog.getTitle());
                }
            }
        }
    }

    <span style="color:#dcc6e0">private</span> List&lt;Blog&gt; <span style="color:#00e0e0">parseJsonData</span><span style="color:#f5ab35">(String jsonData)</span> {
        List&lt;Blog&gt; blogs = <span style="color:#dcc6e0">new</span> ArrayList&lt;&gt;();

        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">try</span> {
            JSONArray jsonArray = <span style="color:#dcc6e0">new</span> JSONArray(jsonData);
            <span style="color:#dcc6e0">for</span> (<span style="color:#dcc6e0">int</span> i = <span style="color:#f5ab35">0</span>; i &lt; jsonArray.length(); i++) {
                JSONObject jsonObject = jsonArray.getJSONObject(i);
                String title = jsonObject.getString(<span style="color:#abe338">&quot;title&quot;</span>);
                String content = jsonObject.getString(<span style="color:#abe338">&quot;content&quot;</span>);

                Blog blog = <span style="color:#dcc6e0">new</span> Blog(title, content);
                blogs.add(blog);
            }
        } <span style="color:#dcc6e0">catch</span> (JSONException e) {
            e.printStackTrace();
        }

        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">return</span> blogs;
    }

    <span style="color:#dcc6e0">private</span> <span style="color:#dcc6e0">class</span> <span style="color:#00e0e0">Blog</span> {
        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">private</span> String title;
        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">private</span> String content;

        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">public</span> <span style="color:#00e0e0">Blog</span><span style="color:#f5ab35">(String title, String content)</span> {
            <span style="color:#dcc6e0">this</span>.title = title;
            <span style="color:#dcc6e0">this</span>.content = content;
        }

        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">public</span> String <span style="color:#00e0e0">getTitle</span><span style="color:#f5ab35">()</span> {
            <span style="color:#dcc6e0">return</span> title;
        }

        <span style="color:#dcc6e0">public</span> String <span style="color:#00e0e0">getContent</span><span style="color:#f5ab35">()</span> {
            <span style="color:#dcc6e0">return</span> content;
        }
    }
}</code></pre>
